Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:35.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終わりが始まるアリアと共に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:40.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白旗を掲げた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:46.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脱獄の果てに歓声の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:50.31,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}手錠突き付けられ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:56.19,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ほら、見て　愚かな駒よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:23:01.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}断罪の茶番
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:03.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}独壇場Funky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:06.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その目で見ろ　競争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.69,0:23:11.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}Forget
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:11.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多発的な展開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.14,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人の波を掻き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:19.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫べ　My Justice，Right Way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:22.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Make it a vow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:24.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感心できるのはFunky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喪失だけが拒止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:32.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}導いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:35.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鮮烈過ぎた年回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:37.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏見のあるカテゴライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:39.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Don't believe no story
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:41.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I know you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:43.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No, we're already over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:45.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Everybody loves despair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:48.94,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I'll sadly go from the end
